OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few bright spells to start
OL,6,Ffor Shetland. Otherwise a rather
OL,7,Fcloudy day with showery outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain. Drier for Orkney later in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Fresh to strong winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA cloudy evening for Shetland
OL,12,Fwith showery outbreaks of rain, but
OL,13,Fdrier and brighter for Orkney. The
OL,14,Frest of the night will see further
OL,15,Fcloud and a few showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
