OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA cloudy day with showery
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, especially for
OL,7,FShetland where rather dull conditions
OL,8,Fwill prevail. Some brighter spells
OL,9,Fpossible for Orkney later. Moderate to
OL,10,Ffresh northwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FHigh
OL,13,Fpressure dominates bringing largely
OL,14,Fsettled but fairly cloudy conditions.
OL,15,FSome bright or sunny spells on Monday
OL,16,Fand Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
